Related Files
app/assets/javascripts/geo.js - Javascript for finding the current location and displaying it on the map
app/assets/javascripts/maps.js - Javascript to find deals for the current location
app/assets/stylesheets/application.css - Styling for the page
app/views/home/index.html.erb - HTML view for the page

Steps to run the app.
1. Open the terminal
2. Change directory to this application's folder
3. Run the following command - "rails server -e production"
4. Open a browser(FireFox/Safari) and enter the following url - "http://localhost:3000/"

This application has been tested on 
FireFox 11.0
Safari Version 5.1.5 (7534.55.3)